| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2735 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8e66fe58-110f-5706-9cb4-66199f49392a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
